# Git Workflow

This project uses standard GitHub pull requests. Do **not** use Gerrit-style pushes.

- Push branches normally: `git push -u origin <branch>`
- Create PRs with `gh pr create`
- Never push to `refs/for/<branch>` — this project does not use Gerrit
